theorem closed_P3_implies_isOpen {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X] {A : Set X} :
    IsClosed A → Topology.P3 A → IsOpen A := by
  intro hClosed hP3
  have hsubset : (A : Set X) ⊆ interior A := by
    dsimp [Topology.P3] at hP3
    simpa [hClosed.closure_eq] using hP3
  have h_eq : (A : Set X) = interior A :=
    Set.Subset.antisymm interior_subset hsubset
  simpa [h_eq] using isOpen_interior

theorem Topology.empty_satisfies_P1_P2_P3 {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X] :
    Topology.P1 (∅ : Set X) ∧ Topology.P2 (∅ : Set X) ∧ Topology.P3 (∅ : Set X) := by
  dsimp [Topology.P1, Topology.P2, Topology.P3]
  simp
